divs: Sighting DetailsMy friend and I were smoking a cigarette outside and i seen something in the sky flickering and beating lights then i noticed another one much like it and they were pretty close together and moving in a way that looked like they were watching us, but when the move it wasn't straight it was up and down when they were moving the objects were much bigger then a star and oddly shaped i was very excited and i went inside to tell everyone an they couldn't explain either i went inside after awhile because it's cold this time of night but that pretty much sums it up.
Summary: seen them for awhile still there hovering and flickering thereslowly going up and and down toward the light
